</div>
<button class="accordion">Why is it necessary to learn about equality, diversity and human rights?</button>
<div class="panel">
<p>Because of the knowledge and respect of rights that students gain from this, combined with understanding, respect and tolerance for difference, can empower them to tackle prejudice, improve relationships and make the most of their lives. In our ever more diverse and challenging society, it becomes more important to instil young people with these positive and open-minded attitudes.</p>
