<button class="accordion">What is the role of the Equality and Human Rights Commission?</button>
<div class="panel">
<p>Equality and Human Rights Commission is the regulatory body responsible for enforcing the Equality Act 2010. Primary duties may include eliminating discrimination and promoting and protecting equality, diversity and human rights</p>
